    "description": "We at Asian Paints Signature Store Consulting Pvt Ltd are looking for an experienced Visual Merchandiser based out of Nashik. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Asian Paints Signature Store Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nAsian Paints Signature Store Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage shrinkage and reduce stock discrepancies\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Train and motivate the sales team to deliver excellent service\n• Maintain high standards of store hygiene and cleanliness\n• Ensure compliance with company policies and retail regulations\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in POS Systems\n• Proficiency in Omnichannel Retail\n• Proficiency in Loyalty Programs\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in Loss Prevention\n• Proficiency in CRM\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Nashik, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Asian Paints Signature Store Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
